name: Destinys Child Beyoncé, Kelly & Michelle Nuclear Bootylicious Superbowl XLVII Hand-Made Tshirt
description:
Nuclear Bootylicious Funk: Can you handle it?

Are you wondering, as we are at Counterfake, how The Dolls of Girl's Tyme will enter the Super Bowl annals of history during this year's half time show?

Well, we've taken some liberties with their new track and concluded that the only way to stack up to Diana and Michael is to take her helicopter and his decoys on a funky/radioactive spaceship to the moon!

Due to the custom nature of this piece, please allow two to three weeks for shirt creation. Expedited orders available as custom orders for $5 extra. Contact us for more information.

Black and primary Jacquard fabric paint and fine-point fabric marker on American Apparel poly-cotton blend. Hand Painted. Sweatshop Free. Made in USA.

While we set the paint with heat, hand wash is recommended to prolong artwork life.
